OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Flynn
OL,6,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,7,Fhas written to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer to call for a four-nation
OL,9,Fsummit on tackling child poverty this
OL,10,Fsummer.
OL,12,FMr Flynn welcomed news the UK
OL,13,FGovernment has set up a ministerial
OL,14,Ftaskforce to kick-start its child
OL,15,Fpoverty strategy, and said it should
OL,16,Fnot delay action on the issue.
