OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Flynn
OL,6,F"The taskforce must not be used as an
OL,7,Fexcuse to delay action.
OL,9,F"Scrapping the cap is the bare minimum
OL,10,Frequired if your Government wants to
OL,11,Fscratch the surface on tackling child
OL,12,Fpoverty, and every day you delay, more
OL,13,Fchildren will suffer the consequences
OL,14,Fof Labour Government inaction.
