OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Flynn
OL,6,F"It is important for the governments
OL,7,Facross the isles to work together on
OL,8,Fthis issue, to move quickly and to
OL,9,Flearn from best practice. I am
OL,10,Ftherefore calling for a four-nations
OL,11,Fsummit on eradicating child poverty
OL,12,Fthis summer.
OL,14,F"I also think it's vital that parties
OL,15,Facross Parliament get the opportunity
OL,16,Fto feed into the taskforce."
