OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Flynn
OL,6,FThe SNP says a package of measures is
OL,7,Fneeded to tackle child poverty,
OL,8,Fincluding matching the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment's Scottish child payment by
OL,10,Fraising universal credit by #26.70 per
OL,11,Fchild, per week across the UK.
OL,13,FEarlier this week, Scottish Secretary
OL,14,FIan Murray said the UK Government
OL,15,Fwants to scrap the two-child benefit
OL,16,Fcap but it cannot afford to yet.
OL,18,FHe told BBC Radio Scotland's Drivetime
OL,19,Fprogramme: "The honest thing to say to
OL,20,Fthe public is we will do this, we want
OL,21,Fto do it.
