OL,3,CFour-nation summit needed now to
OL,4,Ctackle child poverty, says Flynn
OL,6,F"It is something we want to get rid
OL,7,Fof, but we cannot afford to do that
OL,8,Fand we won't make a promise we cannot
OL,9,Fdeliver."
OL,11,FResponding to Mr Flynn's comments, a
OL,12,FUK Government spokesman said: "As the
OL,13,FPM has made clear, no child should be
OL,14,Fin poverty and the Government is
OL,15,Fcommitted to developing an ambitious
OL,16,Fstrategy to reduce child poverty and
OL,17,Fgive children the best start in life.
